# SERVICE

## Greeting

### DESCRIPTION

Greeting service for operation contract testing.

### OPERATION

#### greeting

Returns a greeting for the supplied name.

##### TYPE

QUERY

##### SUMMARY

Return a greeting.

##### DESCRIPTION

Returns a greeting message for the supplied name.

##### ENTITY

Person

##### VISIBILITY

public

##### PRECONDITION

The caller provides a resolvable greeting target.

##### POSTCONDITION

A greeting result is returned without mutating state.

##### RULE

- Greeting generation must remain side-effect free.

##### INPUT

Greeting query payload.

###### SUMMARY

Greeting query payload.

###### DESCRIPTION

Structured query input accepted by greeting.

###### TYPE

GreetingQuery

##### OUTPUT

Greeting result payload.

###### SUMMARY

Greeting result payload.

###### DESCRIPTION

Structured result returned by greeting.

###### TYPE

GreetingResult

# ENTITY

## Person

### ATTRIBUTE

| name | type     | multiplicity |
|------+----------+--------------|
| id   | entityid | 1            |
| name | name     | 1            |
